description: I decided to visit the most famous skating spot in Prague. It was a sunny day so I found many boys practicing their skills. You wouldn´t believe how pretty can skaters be! Eventually I picked a cute boy in a hoodie. He wasn´t a great skater so I tried to flatter him to earn his attention. Which worked perfectly. He totally bought my lie about making a documentary about skater culture in Prague. We had a nice cold drink and talked. The boy was quite open in sharing details from his private life. I knew that I found a really open-minded guy when he agreed to skate around with bare chest. Just one glance at his lean sculptured body made me incredibly horny. I was ready to do anything to get his trousers down. Eventually, it really proved to be a day to remember.
title: Czech Hunter 236
